  "title": "当养猪进入 AI 时代：一个万头猪场如何变革",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDk5NzA0Mw==&mid=2248882551&idx=2&sn=6e36adcdfcf677e68654399597bab93f",
  "date": "2026-03-20 09:47:00",
  "author": "36氪",
